Citation.sTitle: Liquid liquid equilibria of water + 2,3-butanediol + 1-butanol at T = 298.15 K, T = 308.15K and T = 318.15K
Citation.sAbstract: (Liquid liquid) equilibrium (LLE) data of the solubility curves and tie-line compositions have been determined for mixtures of (water + 2,3-  butanediol + 1-butanol) at 298.15, 308.15 and 318.15K and atmospheric pressure. Distribution coefficients and separation factors have been  evaluated for the immiscibility region. The reliability of the experimental tie-lines has been confirmed by using Othmer Tobias correlation. The  LLE data of the ternary systems have been predicted by UNIFAC method.
